overview:
@DisplayName(_ name: String, style: Style = conceptual) Parameters nameThe custom display name.

The text style used to format the symbol’s display name. A value of conceptual (the default) denotes a plain text style that’s not monospaced. A value of symbol denotes a monospaced text style. (optional)

Place the DisplayName directive within a Metadata directive to configure a symbol’s documentation page and any references to that page to show a custom name.
